6. Individually wrapped and sealed pens to sign receipts that guest may take with them.
7. Individually packaged condiments and sealed silverware.
8. Our customers will not have to open doors, as we will have attendees opening every door.

Thank you for all the support during these uncertain times. It has truly been humbling.

To better serve customers, Jet's Pizza is offering Contactless Delivery upon request and Curbside Pick Up at participating locations. During this time, we encourage you to order & pay online, over the phone, or text (where available) to reduce your physical contact with others. With Contactless Delivery, you will not make any person-to-person contact with the person delivering your order, and no signatures will be required if payment and tip are provided online or over the phone. Because we believe that this procedure is safer for both our customers and our delivery drivers, we strongly encourage you to request it when placing your order. Please don't hesitate to instruct our delivery drivers to take a step back or ask to place your pizza at a location you're most comfortable with. We want to ensure your peace of mind & are willing to work with our customers to achieve that. With Curbside Pick Up, you will be notified if your location is offering this service when placing your order. To limit person-to-person contact, submitting your payment online or over the phone is encourage. Once you arrive, please call your Jet's location and they will provide a contactless delivery curbside. In response to this serious health crisis, we enhanced our cleaning and hygiene practices and implemented strict and mandatory health and safety procedures to ensure the highest sanitary standards. Please visit JetPizza.com for more information.

6. Individually wrapped and sealed pens to sign receipts that guest may take with them.
7. Individually packaged condiments and sealed silverware.
8. Our customers will not have to open doors, as we will have attendees opening every door.

And so much more. Thank you for all the support during these uncertain times. It has truly been humbling.

Here are a few precautions we’ll be taking to ensure your well-being as you dine in. We will be operating at 50% capacity to ensure proper social distancing:

3. We will be regularly sanitizing high traffic and high touch areas between customers.
4. Sanitizing stations throughout the restaurant for customers and staff.
5. Disposable menus for each dine in guest. Complimentary mask bags will be provided to every customer.
6. Individually wrapped and sealed pens to sign receipts that guest may take with them.
7. Individually packaged condiments and sealed silverware.

With Curbside Pick Up, you will be notified if your location is offering this service when placing your order. To limit person-to-person contact, submitting your payment online or over the phone is encourage. Once you arrive, please call your Jet's location and they will provide a contactless delivery curbside. In response to this serious health crisis, we enhanced our cleaning and hygiene practices and implemented strict and mandatory health and safety procedures to ensure the highest sanitary standards. Please visit JetPizza.com for more information.
